{"tid":640690,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"由上年開始 每日都用一粒鐘反思人生","createTime":"2018-04-24T12:35:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-24T17:56:41.000Z","uid":8550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dfd96e112e71f5eede1c791c95c63822d72c4d1f","tid":640690,"uid":8550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:35:12.000Z","msg":"而家開始懷疑人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3190ccc56d0c262b452454c0e99c40ca1c410835","tid":640690,"uid":127788,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T12:47:32.000Z","msg":"不要暗戀，去強姦。人生沒有那麼多時間給你演內心戲。愛她就去搞她，喜歡就去強姦。表白有什麼用還是會被拒絕。追不到就下藥，翻臉就發裸照。大不了蹲監獄，你連監獄都不敢蹲還好意思說愛她。出來之後找到她繼續強姦，強姦到讓她開始懷疑自己的人生，讓她覺得她人生的意義就是被你強姦。"},{"pid":"141b6905ad6817438dc4b6e68bc40e6e8cef76d3","tid":640690,"uid":8550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T13:57:17.000Z","msg":"誰是垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91e5517d484b8cf75122c66aebc62b2c12052bad","tid":640690,"uid":34,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T14:01:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e28c62bb5e9d894e4a44654f1618a50f7159885c","tid":640690,"uid":33655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T14:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f0b993c8e5f3461381909cfb800317d44b937d","tid":640690,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T14:45:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f099a5ea3cd46bf69de65b07aaf570bf2ab8fb9a","tid":640690,"uid":8550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T14:57:03.000Z","msg":"其實笑話嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d597922bc21bacf1c770a24123c7c6970d2e04